Document: InputEventMIDI
Path: godot/classes/class_inputeventmidi.rst
Summary: Represents a MIDI input event in Godot.

InputEventMIDI
Inherits: InputEvent < Object

A MIDI input event. This event is generated by devices connected via the Input > MIDI > Input Ports setting.

Properties
----------

